SymmetricWrappedExchange
public static class SymmetricWrappedExchange.ResponseData
extends KeyResponseData

Symmetric key wrapped key response data.

{ "#mandatory" : [ "keyid", "encryptionkey", "hmackey" ], "keyid" : "string", "encryptionkey" : "base64", "hmackey" : "base64" } where:

  • keyid identifies the key that was used to wrap the session keys
  • encryptionkey the Base64-encoded wrapped session encryption key
  • hmackey the Base64-encoded wrapped session HMAC key

Create a new symmetric key wrapped key response data instance with the provided master token, specified key ID and wrapped encryption and HMAC keys.

Parameters:
masterToken - the master token.
keyId - the wrapping key ID.
encryptionKey - the wrapped encryption key.
hmacKey - the wrapped HMAC key.
